cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and emotion recognition from speech and text.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper deals with emotion recognition from facial expressions in videos.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper proposes the use of deep and recurrent neural models for emotion recognition.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is likely as the paper focuses on recognizing emotions in a specific context and the dataset was collected from Youtube videos.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with multimodal emotion recognition from speech, text, and facial expressions in videos.
